# ==========================================================================
# Project-specific
#   - `report/` is a private working-notes folder, kept local
#   - All top-level Markdown other than README.md is scratch / planning
#     (intro.md, todo.md, README_FEASIBILITY.md, etc.)
# ==========================================================================
report/
/*.md
!/README.md

# ==========================================================================
# Visualization scratch — keep committed figures but drop preview renders
# ==========================================================================
figures/_preview/
